{"tid":1431551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有種人 我叫佢地做煙鏟","createTime":"2019-08-08T04:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T11:50:02.000Z","uid":57476,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8b681801d1a12c6ce2132bf45eb18bc0aa42115b","tid":1431551,"uid":57476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:26:27.000Z","msg":"呢種人 就好似一班颱風愛好者咁<br />\n遊行集會一定會岀黎<br />\n但最大目的唔係為咗抗爭<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係為咗食煙</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係為咗po ig story</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為食完煙就有得放上IG/FB屌狗！</span><br />\n<br />\n如果你下次夢見有人帶曬口罩 係你隔離PO IG STORY而又冇記者背心係身<br />\n唔該同佢講一句<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母你不如除口罩啦？</span><br />\n老實你係ig story就係po緊自己係現場嘅record <br />\n你真係以為24小時睇唔到就等於冇咗？你信PO上網嘅野可以完全冇record？<br />\n<br />\n保護自己 手足我地一句都不能少！唔好再做自殺行為好冇！"},{"pid":"c1b65a4ea8448f4ae38edd77ea0a9ada54b6260a","tid":1431551,"uid":57476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:30:24.000Z","msg":"SORRY 係一個都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a495169e5379b725baf078a84cdea621b862794","tid":1431551,"uid":213059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:35:01.000Z","msg":"On9 出嚟抗爭以為好撚好玩 打曬卡咁<br />\n唔撚洗拉你都知你有份係現場啦 <br />\n淨係非法集結都夠鋤死你"},{"pid":"3eafce591e820733cc73ab6e436f683d2cc82419","tid":1431551,"uid":57476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:44:27.000Z","msg":"前線真心有人為撚狗而岀 狗係無恥 但我地係要對準政權呀 勿忘初心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c64ecc34917664478ac533f5b98f8095d0a6b7","tid":1431551,"uid":190604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:45:56.000Z","msg":"覺得係合法遊行集會嘅時候post係無咩問題，但完咗對恃緊個陣就算啦唔好搞咁多嘢<br />\n<br />\n不過人地鐘意咁做咪由佢囉，寧願佢有出嚟打卡好過無出嚟"},{"pid":"36c1ab9c50029da55c25874c67a9d08f0772e72e","tid":1431551,"uid":1060,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:54:00.000Z","msg":"屌屌下就愈黎愈少人出黎<br />\n和理非好 出黎食煙又好 剩係識係IG post story又好<br />\n其實多個人出黎充人數 虛張聲勢都好有效<br />\n而家搞到個個自我審查 <br />\n有時我自己都心諗：死啦 我出到去又唔上前線 無貢獻仲應唔應該出黎？"},{"pid":"6e07498dae90cab7242c3fbf631aa6a7225b06ec","tid":1431551,"uid":1060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:55:00.000Z","msg":"Be water 唔單止行動上 我認為思想上都應該要應用到囉"},{"pid":"85b3f8b7722934d9e8f2f2634ab5c9a83047d1b0","tid":1431551,"uid":128522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:08:30.000Z","msg":"有種人, 我叫佢四方閪<br />\n呢樣又唔撚得, 果樣又潔僻<br />\n<br />\n依家最緊係係人數, 人頭呀<br />\n屌走晒D人好咩"},{"pid":"1e58fbecca4783b25f54e15eb76e34c123e65906","tid":1431551,"uid":57476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85b3f8b7722934d9e8f2f2634ab5c9a83047d1b0","tid":1431551,"uid":128522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:08:30.000Z","msg":"有種人, 我叫佢四方閪<br />\n呢樣又唔撚得, 果樣又潔僻<br />\n<br />\n依家最緊係係人數, 人頭呀<br />\n屌走晒D人好咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:50:02.000Z","msg":"絕對唔係迫全民皆兵 <span style=\"color: red;\">和理非同勇武缺一不可</span><br />\n但老實 著住條裙帶個口罩岀黎打卡嘅人 有事上黎要人救 一係對自己唔負責任 二係對大家都唔負責任呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}